lead_paragraph: The Denver Broncos won their third National Football League championship with a 24-10 upset victory over the top-seeded Carolina Panthers in Super Bowl 50 on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Broncos Defense Dominates Panthers to Win Super Bowl
